    <head>
        <drug>
            <atcs>
                <atc>J01XA01</atc>
            </atcs>
            <activeSubstances>
                <activeSubstance>vancomycin</activeSubstance>
            </activeSubstances>
            <drugName>
                <name lang='en'>Vancomycin</name>
            </drugName>
            <drugDescription>
                <desc lang='en'>Vancomycin is an antibiotic of the glycopeptide family, used to treat a number of bacterial infections. It is usually given intravenously as either intermittent or continuous infusions for the treatment of complicated skin infections, bloodstream infections, endocarditis, bone and joint infections, meningitis etc. It is particularly useful to combat methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus aureus, as well as various strains of Enterococcus. Vancomycin is a typical drug necessitating dosage adjustment by TDM. Oral treatment for severe Clostridium difficile colitis does not deserve TDM as the drug is poorly absorbed in the gut.</desc>
            </drugDescription>
            <tdmStrategy>
                <text lang='en'>The efficacy of vancomycin is best predicted by the AUC of circulating concentrations over MIC of the target bacteria. The MIC of most sensitive bacterias is below 1 mg/L, a value usually considered when the actual MIC of the bacterial strain infecting the patient has not been determined. The most usual recommendation regarding AUC/MIC value in the literature is to keep it above 400 h over a one-day interval. This can equivalently be expressed in terms of average concentration with a corresponding minimum target of 17 times the MIC, or 17 mg/L assuming a MIC of 1 mg/L. We use practically a target of 500 h, with an acceptance interval of 400 to 700 h. Accordingly, the concentration target that we recommend for a continuous infusion is 15-25 mg/L.
                                                Another traditional method of dosage optimization often proposed for vancomycin given as intermittent infusion is to target a trough concentration of 10-15 mg/L. Yet a higher target of 15-20 mg/L is recommended for MRSA and other severe infections with Enterococcus of high resistance potential.  </text>
            </tdmStrategy>
        </drug>
        <study>
            <studyName>
                <name lang='en'>Optimisation of vancomycin exposure in neonates based on the best level of evidence</name>
            </studyName>
            <studyAuthors>Dao K, Guidi M, André P, Giannoni E, Basterrechea S, Zhao W, Fuchs A, Pfister M, Buclin T, Csajka C.</studyAuthors>
            <description>
                <desc lang='en'>A total 405 neonates provided 1831 vancomycin concentrations measured during routine TDM. A one-compartment model with linear elimination incorporating covariates such as age, kidney function and body weight was developed with NONMEM. The final model was applied to simulate in our population vancomycin exposure resulting from 20 dosing guidelines identified in the literature.</desc>
            </description>
            <references>
                <reference type='bibtex'>
                    <![CDATA[% 31108184
                    @Article{pmid31108184,
                       Author="Dao, K.  and Guidi, M.  and Andr?, P.  and Giannoni, E.  and Basterrechea, S.  and Zhao, W.  and Fuchs, A.  and Pfister, M.  and Buclin, T.  and Csajka, C. ",
                       Title="{{O}ptimisation of vancomycin exposure in neonates based on the best level of evidence}",
                       Journal="Pharmacol. Res.",
                       Year="2019",
                       Pages="104278",
                       Month="May"
                    }
                    ]]>
                </reference>
            </references>
        </study>
        <comments/>
    </head>
    <drugModel>
        <drugId>vancomycin</drugId>
        <drugModelId>ch.tucuxi.vancomycin.dao2019</drugModelId>
        <domain>
            <description>
                <desc lang='en'>Neonates up to 6 months, intermittent IV vancomycin</desc>
            </description>
            <constraints/>
        </domain>
        <covariates>
            <covariate>
                <covariateId>ga</covariateId>
                <covariateName>
                    <name lang='en'>Gestational age</name>
                </covariateName>
                <description>
                    <desc lang='en'>Age in weeks between the last menstrual period of the mother and the birth of the patient</desc>
                </description>
                <unit>week</unit>
                <covariateType>standard</covariateType>
                <dataType>double</dataType>
                <interpolationType>linear</interpolationType>
                <refreshPeriod>
                    <unit>w</unit>
                    <value>1</value>
                </refreshPeriod>
                <covariateValue>
                    <standardValue>40</standardValue>
                </covariateValue>
                <validation>
                    <errorMessage>
                        <text lang='fr'>Gestational age must be between 20 and 45 weeks</text>
                    </errorMessage>
                    <operation>
                        <softFormula>
                            <inputs>
                                <input>
                                    <id>ga</id>
                                    <type>double</type>
                                </input>
                            </inputs>
                            <code>
                                <![CDATA[return ((ga > 20) && (ga < 45));]]>
                                </code>
                            </softFormula>
                            <comments/>
                        </operation>
                        <comments/>
                    </validation>
                    <comments>
                        <comment lang='en'>
                        </comment>
                    </comments>
                </covariate>
                <covariate>
                    <covariateId>ageInWeeks</covariateId>
                    <covariateName>
                        <name lang='en'>Post-natal age in weeks</name>
                    </covariateName>
                    <description>
                        <desc lang='en'>Post-natal age in weeks</desc>
                    </description>
                    <unit>week</unit>
                    <covariateType>ageInWeeks</covariateType>
                    <dataType>double</dataType>
                    <interpolationType>linear</interpolationType>
                    <refreshPeriod>
                        <unit>d</unit>
                        <value>1</value>
                    </refreshPeriod>
                    <covariateValue>
                        <standardValue>1</standardValue>
                    </covariateValue>
                    <validation>
                        <errorMessage>
                            <text lang='fr'>Postnatal age must be less than 30 weeks</text>
                        </errorMessage>
                        <operation>
                            <softFormula>
                                <inputs>
                                    <input>
                                        <id>ageInWeeks</id>
                                        <type>double</type>
                                    </input>
                                </inputs>
                                <code>
                                    <![CDATA[return (ageInWeeks < 30);]]>
                                    </code>
                                </softFormula>
                                <comments/>
                            </operation>
                            <comments/>
                        </validation>
                        <comments>
                            <comment lang='en'>
                            </comment>
                        </comments>
                    </covariate>
                    <covariate>
                        <covariateId>bodyweight</covariateId>
                        <covariateName>
                            <name lang='en'>Body weight in kg</name>
                        </covariateName>
                        <description>
                            <desc lang='en'>Body weight in kg</desc>
                        </description>
                        <unit>kg</unit>
                        <covariateType>standard</covariateType>
                        <dataType>double</dataType>
                        <interpolationType>linear</interpolationType>
                        <refreshPeriod>
                            <unit>d</unit>
                            <value>1</value>
                        </refreshPeriod>
                        <covariateValue>
                            <standardValue>3</standardValue>
                        </covariateValue>
                        <validation>
                            <errorMessage>
                                <text lang='fr'>Body weight must be between 0.4 and 8 kg</text>
                            </errorMessage>
                            <operation>
                                <softFormula>
                                    <inputs>
                                        <input>
                                            <id>bodyweight</id>
                                            <type>double</type>
                                        </input>
                                    </inputs>
                                    <code>
                                        <![CDATA[return ((bodyweight > 0.4) && (bodyweight < 8));]]>
                                        </code>
                                    </softFormula>
                                    <comments/>
                                </operation>
                                <comments/>
                            </validation>
                            <comments>
                                <comment lang='en'>
                                </comment>
                            </comments>
                        </covariate>
                        <covariate>
                            <covariateId>creatinine</covariateId>
                            <covariateName>
                                <name lang='en'>Creatinine </name>
                            </covariateName>
                            <description>
                                <desc lang='en'>Creatinine in µmol/L</desc>
                            </description>
                            <unit>umol/l</unit>
                            <!-- <unit>µmol/L</unit> -->
                            <covariateType>standard</covariateType>
                            <dataType>double</dataType>
                            <interpolationType>linear</interpolationType>
                            <refreshPeriod>
                                <unit>d</unit>
                                <value>1</value>
                            </refreshPeriod>
                            <covariateValue>
                                <standardValue>35</standardValue>
                            </covariateValue>
                            <validation>
                                <errorMessage>
                                    <text lang='en'>Creatinine must be between 10 and 500 µmol/L</text>
                                </errorMessage>
                                <operation>
                                    <softFormula>
                                        <inputs>
                                            <input>
                                                <id>creatinine</id>
                                                <type>double</type>
                                            </input>
                                        </inputs>
                                        <code>
                                            <![CDATA[return ((creatinine > 9) && (creatinine < 501));]]>
                                            </code>
                                        </softFormula>
                                        <comments/>
                                    </operation>
                                    <comments/>
                                </validation>
                                <comments>
                                    <comment lang='en'>
                                    </comment>
                                </comments>
                            </covariate>
                        </covariates>
                        <activeMoieties>
                            <activeMoiety>
                                <activeMoietyId>vancomycin</activeMoietyId>
                                <activeMoietyName>
                                    <name lang='en'>vancomycin</name>
                                </activeMoietyName>
                                <unit>mg/l</unit>
                                <analyteIdList>
                                    <analyteId>vancomycin</analyteId>
                                </analyteIdList>
                                <analytesToMoietyFormula>
                                    <hardFormula>direct</hardFormula>
                                    <comments/>
                                </analytesToMoietyFormula>
                                <targets>
                                    <target>
                                        <targetType>auc24</targetType>
                                        <targetValues>
                                            <unit>mg*h/l</unit>
                                            <min>
                                                <standardValue>400</standardValue>
                                            </min>
                                            <max>
                                                <standardValue>700</standardValue>
                                            </max>
                                            <best>
                                                <standardValue>530</standardValue>
                                            </best>
                                            <toxicityAlarm>
                                                <standardValue>100</standardValue>
                                            </toxicityAlarm>
                                            <inefficacyAlarm>
                                                <standardValue>1000</standardValue>
                                            </inefficacyAlarm>
                                        </targetValues>
                                        <comments/>
                                    </target>
                                </targets>
                            </activeMoiety>
                        </activeMoieties>
                        <analyteGroups>
                            <analyteGroup>
                                <groupId>vancomycin</groupId>
                                <pkModelId>linear.1comp.macro</pkModelId>
                                <analytes>
                                    <analyte>
                                        <analyteId>vancomycin</analyteId>
                                        <unit>mg/l</unit>
                                        <molarMass>
                                            <value>1449.3</value>
                                            <unit>g/mol</unit>
                                        </molarMass>
                                        <description>
                                            <desc lang='en'>
                                            </desc>
                                        </description>
                                        <errorModel>
                                            <errorModelType>mixed</errorModelType>
                                            <sigmas>
                                                <sigma>
                                                    <standardValue>1.98</standardValue>
                                                </sigma>
                                                <sigma>
                                                    <standardValue>0.236</standardValue>
                                                </sigma>
                                            </sigmas>
                                            <comments/>
                                        </errorModel>
                                        <comments/>
                                    </analyte>
                                </analytes>
                                <dispositionParameters>
                                    <parameters>
                                        <parameter>
                                            <parameterId>CL</parameterId>
                                            <unit>l/h</unit>
                                            <parameterValue>
                                                <standardValue>0.273</standardValue>
                                                <aprioriComputation>
                                                    <softFormula>
                                                        <inputs>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>ageInWeeks</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>ga</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>bodyweight</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>creatinine</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                        </inputs>
                                                        <code>
                                                            <![CDATA[median_BW = 1;
                                                            median_creat = 54;
                                                            Hill = 3.54;
                                                            T50 = 46.4;
                                                            PMA = ga + ageInWeeks;
                                                            theta_CL = 0.273;
                                                            theta_BW = 0.438;
                                                            theta_creat = 0.473;
                                                            cl1 = theta_CL * Math.pow((bodyweight/median_BW),theta_BW);
                                                            cl2 = cl1 * Math.pow((median_creat/creatinine),theta_creat);
                                                            cl3 = cl2 * (Math.pow(PMA,Hill) / (Math.pow(PMA,Hill) + Math.pow(T50,Hill)));
                                                            if (cl3 < 0) {
                                                              cl3 = 0.001;
                                                            }
                                                            return cl3;]]>
                                                        </code>
                                                    </softFormula>
                                                    <comments/>
                                                </aprioriComputation>
                                            </parameterValue>
                                            <bsv>
                                                <bsvType>exponential</bsvType>
                                                <stdDevs>
                                                    <stdDev>0.226</stdDev>
                                                </stdDevs>
                                            </bsv>
                                            <validation>
                                                <errorMessage>
                                                    <text lang='fr'>
                                                    </text>
                                                </errorMessage>
                                                <operation>
                                                    <softFormula>
                                                        <inputs>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>CL</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                        </inputs>
                                                        <code>
                                                            <![CDATA[
                                                            return CL > 0.0;
                                                            ]]>
                                                        </code>
                                                    </softFormula>
                                                    <comments/>
                                                </operation>
                                                <comments/>
                                            </validation>
                                            <comments/>
                                        </parameter>
                                        <parameter>
                                            <parameterId>V</parameterId>
                                            <unit>l</unit>
                                            <parameterValue>
                                                <standardValue>0.628</standardValue>
                                                <aprioriComputation>
                                                    <softFormula>
                                                        <inputs>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>bodyweight</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                        </inputs>
                                                        <code>
                                                            <![CDATA[median_BW = 1;
                                                            theta_V = 0.628;
                                                            v1 = theta_V * bodyweight/median_BW;
                                                            if (v1 < 0) {
                                                              v1 = 0.001;
                                                            }
                                                            return v1;
                                                            ]]>
                                                        </code>
                                                    </softFormula>
                                                    <comments/>
                                                </aprioriComputation>
                                            </parameterValue>
                                            <bsv>
                                                <bsvType>none</bsvType>
                                            </bsv>
                                            <validation>
                                                <errorMessage>
                                                    <text lang='fr'>
                                                    </text>
                                                </errorMessage>
                                                <operation>
                                                    <softFormula>
                                                        <inputs>
                                                            <input>
                                                                <id>V</id>
                                                                <type>double</type>
                                                            </input>
                                                        </inputs>
                                                        <code>
                                                            <![CDATA[
                                                            return V > 0.0;
                                                            ]]>
                                                        </code>
                                                    </softFormula>
                                                    <comments/>
                                                </operation>
                                                <comments/>
                                            </validation>
                                            <comments/>
                                        </parameter>
                                    </parameters>
                                    <correlations/>
                                </dispositionParameters>
                            </analyteGroup>
                        </analyteGroups>
                        <formulationAndRoutes default='id0'>
                            <formulationAndRoute>
                                <formulationAndRouteId>id0</formulationAndRouteId>
                                <formulation>parenteralSolution</formulation>
                                <administrationName>Intermittent intravenous infusion</administrationName>
                                <administrationRoute>intravenousDrip</administrationRoute>
                                <absorptionModel>infusion</absorptionModel>
                                <dosages>
                                    <analyteConversions>
                                        <analyteConversion>
                                            <analyteId>vancomycin</analyteId>
                                            <factor>1</factor>
                                        </analyteConversion>
                                    </analyteConversions>
                                    <availableDoses>
                                        <unit>mg</unit>
                                        <default>
                                            <standardValue>45</standardValue>
                                        </default>
                                        <rangeValues>
                                            <from>
                                                <standardValue>2</standardValue>
                                            </from>
                                            <to>
                                                <standardValue>200</standardValue>
                                            </to>
                                            <step>
                                                <standardValue>1</standardValue>
                                            </step>
                                        </rangeValues>
                                    </availableDoses>
                                    <availableIntervals>
                                        <unit>h</unit>
                                        <default>
                                            <standardValue>8</standardValue>
                                        </default>
                                        <fixedValues>
                                            <value>4</value>
                                            <value>6</value>
                                            <value>8</value>
                                            <value>12</value>
                                            <value>18</value>
                                            <value>24</value>
                                            <value>36</value>
                                            <value>48</value>
                                            <value>72</value>
                                        </fixedValues>
                                    </availableIntervals>
                                    <availableInfusions>
                                        <unit>min</unit>
                                        <default>
                                            <standardValue>60</standardValue>
                                        </default>
                                        <fixedValues>
                                            <value>30</value>
                                            <value>60</value>
                                            <value>120</value>
                                        </fixedValues>
                                    </availableInfusions>
                                    <comments/>
                                </dosages>
                                <absorptionParameters/>
                            </formulationAndRoute>
                        </formulationAndRoutes>
                        <timeConsiderations>
                            <halfLife>
                                <unit>h</unit>
                                <duration>
                                    <standardValue>4</standardValue>
                                </duration>
                                <multiplier>15</multiplier>
                                <comments>
                                    <comment lang='en'>
                                    </comment>
                                </comments>
                            </halfLife>
                            <outdatedMeasure>
                                <unit>d</unit>
                                <duration>
                                    <standardValue>15</standardValue>
                                </duration>
                                <comments>
                                    <comment lang='en'>
                                    </comment>
                                </comments>
                            </outdatedMeasure>
                        </timeConsiderations>
                        <comments/>
                    </drugModel>
                </model>
